===================
GAME OF LIFE README
===================


-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
RUNNING CODE
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TO SUBMIT JOB, RECOMPILE, AND RUN [ON GRAPE]: 
--------------------------------------------
    --> RUN : qsub life.cmd

TO RECOMPILE AND RUN:
---------------------
    --> RUN : ./run.sh

TO COMPILE: 
-----------
    To Clean: 
        --> RUN : make clean 

    To Compile: 
        --> RUN : make

    Makefile
    --------
        -- src/ dirctory contains all the necessary .f90 files.
        -- build/ directory contains the .o and .mod files from build.

        NOTE ON COMPILER :
            - If the default compiler for mpif90 is

                = gfortran : [GRAPE] 
                      Ensure the flag specifying the build directory is a '-J' s.t. the line it reads 
                            $(OBJDIR)/%.o: $(SRCDIR)/%.f90 
                                    'mpif90 -c $< -o $@ -J $(OBJDIR)'

                = ifort : [OTHER] 
                      Ensure the flag specifying the build directory is a '-module' s.t. the line it reads 
                            $(OBJDIR)/%.o: $(SRCDIR)/%.f90 
                                    'mpif90 -c $< -o $@ -module $(OBJDIR)'

TO RUN USING MPIRUN:
--------------------
    --> RUN : mpirun -np {np} main.exe


